headline: Spotting Winners: Fastly (NYSE:FSLY) And Content Delivery Stocks In Q4
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Fastly (NYSE:FSLY) and the best and worst performers in the content delivery industry.
